author: AGENCIES
title: Rosie Huntington-Whiteley reveals she's pregnant with Jason Statham's child
text: Rosie Huntington-Whiteley British model and actress Rosie Huntington-Whiteley who is currently engaged to actor Jason Statham, has confirmed rumours of her pregnancy with a post on Instagram. Posting a photo of herself with a baby bump clearly visible, Rosie captioned the image “Very happy to share that Jason and I are expecting!! Lots of love Rosie. Photo by @jasonstatham (sic)”. Rumours of the pregnancy first started earlier this year, when Rosie had posted another photo of herself on Instagram where she wrote, “Here’s to fresh starts and exciting prospects for the new year,” that sources had claimed to be about a pregnancy.
